  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency unminified-webpack-plugin to v1.4.1",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin\">unminified-webpack-plugin</a> from <code>v1.2.0</code> to <code>v1.4.1</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"141\">1.4.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/44a763108d0ba72fd81e2b1297c85cdb6f2caa87\"><code>44a7631</code></a> Update version and engine restriction</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/68be9e38c2e8ddc4e80c822780b04df965651844\"><code>68be9e3</code></a> Fix: rollback syntax to have node6 supported</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"140\">1.4.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/cae981348c1e2b27b4c1c15e6cfb0a14dc324b76\"><code>cae9813</code></a> Update .travis.yml to only support node 8+</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/968019bee46bbc063dde2a981fd10c313a7bb469\"><code>968019b</code></a> magic for bannerPlugin support</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"130\">1.3.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/e3ea5f1671ceac5bfd3931ce40265ea4834e752f\"><code>e3ea5f1</code></a> Support extract-text-webpack-plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/78444196db309e72e7a8d57dc4b05947c7feee65\"><code>7844419</code></a> update dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/76c397c4451821ae5252f507771907debf504ff4\"><code>76c397c</code></a> add more tests for include/exclude options</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/d53d4833531e3301fbcfb117df26d21d5d888528\"><code>d53d483</code></a> adjust doc format</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/leftstick/unminified-webpack-plugin/commit/c8c307fe8ef3ea8edb0bcac9966a3ba7a0bff0aa\"><code>c8c307f</code></a> update documentation</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
